    "If organizations seeking such customization have large volumes of content, they also need to apply vector databases or content similarity algorithms to feed the customized content selectively into the model.",
    "Customization using a company's own content requires that the content is well-curated and of high quality, currency, uniqueness, and so forth (Davenport & Tiwari, 2024).",
